Summary: Large white object of indeterminate shape emmiting very low frequency hum.also two small balls of light,one amber one red
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile walking down a dark street I saw two balls of light advancing toward me,one amber one red.I first took them to be head and brake lights from a car on the nearby parkway but they came right at me in an up and down motion.they stopped when I back-tracked and advanced when i moved forward.Not wanting to turn my back to them I walked back wardsto the end of the street.I then walked around a few blocks to get to the other end of this street.As I approached the corner I became aware of a very low frequency hum and a flickering light in the sky,it was as if the whole atmosphere was vibrating.I then noticed two balls of light about the size of softballs once again advancing toward me.Again I backed away and they went out.I then noticed to my right a large white object behind some trees. icould not determine its shape through the trees.It was not glowing just a non reflecting white.At this point I felt A bit scared and that I had seen enough.I felt like I shouldn,t be seeing this-Like something was warning me to stay away.My fear now overcoming my curiosity I fled and went home.I felt tired and weak the next day.My teeth hurt for several days.I think the low frequency hum loosended my fillings.
